# MISC::PLM_IS_IN_CONSTRAINED_MODE

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns true if we're in the constrained PLM (Process Lifetime Management) mode (executing with reduced CPU/GPU allocation)

aka "constrained"
